```plantuml
@startuml vishipayyallore_blazorwasm-apim-api-sql-redis

actor User
participant "Blazor WebAssembly" as Blazor
participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "ASP.NET Core API" as API
participant "Business Logic Layer" as BLL
participant "Cache Layer (Redis)" as Cache
participant "Database Layer (SQL Server)" as Database

User -> Blazor: Interact with Web UI
Blazor -> APIGateway: Send HTTP Request (Get Book Details)
APIGateway -> API: Forward Request
API -> BLL: Call GetBookDetails()
BLL -> Cache: Check Cache for Book
alt Book in Cache
    Cache -> BLL: Return Book Data
else Book not in Cache
    BLL -> Database: Query Book
    Database -> BLL: Return Book Data
    BLL -> Cache: Update Cache with Book Data
end
BLL -> API: Return Book Data
API -> APIGateway: Forward Response
APIGateway -> Blazor: Return Book Data
Blazor -> User: Display Book Details

@enduml
```